  "description": "Small, bright, competitive. A shallow pocket of warm water where everything fights for space. Square barnacles and noise turbulence through a resonant pool. High competition strength means any coupled engine must fight for sonic territory. The reef ducks, breathes, and reasserts on every transient.",
